author: wn.com
title: Refugee crisis: David Cameron urged to ensure vulnerable Syrian refugees are settled by winter
text: David Cameron must “break the deadlock” between government and local councils to ensure 1, 000 of the most vulnerable Syrian refugees are settled before freezing winter temperatures take their toll on refugee camps, campaigners have warned.
